<div class="ep-source cDGray" style="padding-top: 6px; padding-bottom: 6px; margin-top: 24px; color: #727171; float: right; font-size: 12px; line-height: 13px; font-family: ''Sim sun''; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;"><span class="left" style="float: left;"><a style="color: #0f6b99; text-decoration-line: underline;" href="http://news.163.com/"><img class="icon" style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; margin-left: 2px;" src="https://static.ws.126.net/cnews/css13/img/end_news.png" alt="林启辉" width="13" height="12" /></a>&nbsp;本文来源：央视新闻客户端</span><span class="ep-editor" style="float: right; white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 25px;">责任编辑：林启辉_NB13068</span></div>', null, null, 1, null, null, 0, null, null, 3, null, null, null, '1', 'admin', '2020-05-31 09:52:28', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO cms.t_article (id, article_title, sub_title, type_id, type_name, simple_intro, content, title_color, bold_flag, review_flag, top_flag, ad_flag, delete_flag, recommend_flag, keyword, status, delete_no, delete_name, delete_time, add_no, add_name, add_time, update_no, update_name, update_time) VALUES (11, '全美周六爆发示威，特朗普和彭斯去哪儿了？', '（原标题：全美周六爆发示威，特朗普和彭斯下午一起观看载人飞船发射）', 2, null, '', '<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">【文/观察者网】美国非裔黑人弗洛伊德被暴力执法&ldquo;锁喉&rdquo;致死后，愤怒的美国人走上街头抗议示威，暴力蔓延至全美30多座城市。抗议者甚至已集结在白宫前与防暴警察激烈对峙。而另一方面，特朗普在推特上严厉警告示威者的同时，不忘与彭斯前往佛罗里达观看&ldquo;龙&rdquo;飞船的载人火箭发射。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">3天前，因天公不作美，发射任务被临时取消。但肯尼迪航天中心没有再次让特朗普失望&mdash;&mdash;美东时间5月30日下午，美国太空探索技术公司（SpaceX）的&ldquo;猎鹰9&rdquo;号火箭从佛罗里达州肯尼迪航天中心成功发射。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">彭斯妻子兴奋地鼓起了掌，并拉起右侧彭斯的手，两人交谈着。而画面最右侧的特朗普则表现得比较淡定。</p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/547eac60j00qb6rg20081c001kw011wc.jpg" /></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="text-align: justify;">（彭斯 推特）</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&ldquo;你们混凝土跑道的裂缝里长出了杂草&mdash;&mdash;不美观，根本不美观，&rdquo;再次来到佛罗里达的特朗普在发射后的演讲上抱怨着，但是他难以掩饰兴奋，说&ldquo;这次发射成功，标志着（美国航天）失去的、不作为数十年正式结束&hellip;&hellip;&rdquo;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">特朗普不忘吹嘘自己比起前任总统们的过人之处，他说，&ldquo;以往的领导人想把宇航员送上太空，需要仰仗其他国家的帮助&mdash;&mdash;而这种情况不会再有了。&rdquo;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">美国国家公共广播电台（NPR）5月30日发文，题为&ldquo;<span style="font-weight: bold; list-style: none;">特朗普把10年前就开始的太空计划的功劳占为己有</span>&rdquo;。文章称，&ldquo;实际上，是过去的两任总统将NASA扶上正轨，才有了这次SpaceX的发射成功。但是如果听发射后的演讲，很容易忽视这一点。&rdquo;</p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/4a34d431p00qb6rg2000mc000k1004ic.png" /></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="text-align: justify;">（NPR报道截图）</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">彭斯的发言则较为谄媚，&ldquo;今天，是3年半间，让太空领导权重回美国行动的高潮。&rdquo;他将此次发射称为<span style="font-weight: bold; list-style: none;">&ldquo;</span><span style="font-weight: bold; list-style: none;">总统远见卓识与领导才华的体现</span><span style="font-weight: bold; list-style: none;">&rdquo;</span>（a tribute to the vision and leadership of a president who&hellip;&hellip;）。彭斯称，从特朗普总统执政的第一天，他就决心要重振NASA和美国在人类空间探索方面的领袖地位。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">在30日总统与副总统与马斯克的SpaceX公司一起&ldquo;仰望太空&rdquo;的同时，美国大陆上，30多座城市的暴力示威行动则让全美陷入水深火热之中。同日的华盛顿特区，示威者在白宫西北侧的艾森豪威尔行政楼外，与大批警察展开激烈对峙。他们高喊&ldquo;我无法呼吸&rdquo;，愤怒的示威者将防护栏拆除。防暴警察使用了胡椒弹，双方剑拔弩张。记者统计示威者已达数千人。</p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/3539615dp00qb6rg300jvc000j800cfc.png" /></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="text-align: justify;">（图源 央视新闻）</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">事实上，从29日下午起，示威的洪水就已涌向白宫门口。示威者们试图越过路障，冲击特勤局特工的防暴盾牌，并破坏车辆，特工则用警棍和辣椒喷雾剂予以回击。直至30日凌晨3点多，冲突才逐渐平息。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">特朗普此时还在白宫内。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">他于30日一早，连发4推表扬了特工们的&ldquo;英勇&rdquo;，称他们&ldquo;很棒很酷&rdquo;，并说&ldquo;我在白宫里注视着每一个人的一举一动，感到无比的安全。&rdquo;同时他警告示威者如果冲破白宫围栏，那么&ldquo;<span style="font-weight: bold; list-style: none;">迎接他们的将是最凶恶的狗，以及我所见过的最凶狠的武器。</span>&rdquo;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">此后，他再次前往佛罗里达州的肯尼迪航天中心等待火箭的发射。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">在即将发射前，他在推特上试图掀起明尼苏达州的示威活动的&ldquo;阴谋论&rdquo;，用大写字母将示威者们称为&ldquo;暴徒&rdquo;（RIOTERS），武断地认为他们&ldquo;来自州外势力&rdquo;。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">随即，他的推特又&ldquo;画风一转&rdquo;，流露出他对即将发射火箭的兴奋，希望火箭发射安全、成功。并@了福克斯新闻以及同样和特朗普关系不错的美国第一新闻网（OANN）。</p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/8c7e87f5p00qb6rg2000ic000gl0033c.png" /></p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">2015年时，特朗普曾发推特称，&ldquo;如果道琼斯单日跌超1000点，现任总统应当被塞到大炮里，以极快的速度被射向太阳。&rdquo;今年，美股见证了历史性的4次熔断，许多网友表示应该让特朗普&ldquo;上天&rdquo;。</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">现在，&ldquo;抗疫&rdquo;不力与&ldquo;抗议&rdquo;升级的怒火让网友又玩起了&ldquo;火箭梗&rdquo;。在《国会山报》的相关推特新闻下，数十名网友表示要将特朗普&ldquo;送上太空。&rdquo;</p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/2a3f0a36p00qb6rg2004zc000gn00ejc.png" /></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="text-align: justify;">（网友恶搞 &ldquo;他没在上面真遗憾&rdquo;）</span></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><img style="vertical-align: top; border: 0px; max-width: 550px;" src="https://cms-bucket.ws.126.net/2020/0531/f73fb0a9p00qb6rg2004kc000gm00azc.png" /></p>
<p class="f_center" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040; text-align: center; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="text-align: justify;">（网友恶搞推特）</span></p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">以非裔美国人弗洛伊德之死引发的骚乱已蔓延至全美30多座城市。&ldquo;震中&rdquo;明尼阿波利斯市千疮百孔；亚特兰大CNN总部大楼被砸；累计有数十人被逮捕，其中包括CNN记者；至少有2名美国人在骚乱中被枪击。目前国民警卫队已开始加大兵力部署，五角大楼也在调配宪兵，防止事态进一步升级。</p>', null, null, 1, null, null, 0, null, null, 3, null, null, null, '1', 'admin', '2020-05-31 09:52:56', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO cms.t_article (id, article_title, sub_title, type_id, type_name, simple_intro, content, title_color, bold_flag, review_flag, top_flag, ad_flag, delete_flag, recommend_flag, keyword, status, delete_no, delete_name, delete_time, add_no, add_name, add_time, update_no, update_name, update_time) VALUES (12, '秋冬是否会出现第二波疫情？张文宏：有可能反弹', '（原标题：张文宏回应秋冬是否会出现第二波疫情）', 2, null, '', '<p class="otitle" style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<div class="video-wrapper" style="margin: 10px auto; color: #404040; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; background: #f5f5f5;">
<div class="video-inner" style="padding: 25px 25px 20px;">
<div class="video" style="background: #000000; max-height: 450px;"><video style="height: 344.078px; max-height: 450px;" poster="https://videoimg.nos-jd.163yun.com/cmssnapshot/20200531/iprM11172_0.jpg" preload="auto" controls="controls" width="100%"></video></div>
<div class="video-info clearfix" style="margin-top: 16px; height: 20px; line-height: 20px;">
<p class="fn-right" style="font-size: 12px; height: 22px; line-height: 22px; overflow: hidden; float: right;"><a class="video-title" style="color: #000000; text-align: right; float: left; width: 300px;" href="https://v.163.com/static/3/VKD1LS143.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">张文宏回应秋冬是否会出现第二波疫情</a><span class="video-from" style="color: #a7a7a7; margin-left: 10px;">（来源：环球网）</span></p>
</div>
<div class="video-list">&nbsp;</div>
</div>
</div>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;">【#张文宏回应秋冬是否会出现第二波疫情#】张文宏：当前，很多国家的疫情还在快速蔓延。在这种情况下复工复产，疫情控制不太好的国家，其整体的发病人数很难控制下来，特别到了秋冬季，疫情就可能反弹。不过大家不用过于担心，我国应对疫情的体系非常完整，已为防范疫情输入做好了准备。</p>', null, null, 1, null, null, 0, null, null, 3, null, null, null, '1', 'admin', '2020-05-31 09:53:25', null, null, null);
INSERT INTO cms.t_article (id, article_title, sub_title, type_id, type_name, simple_intro, content, title_color, bold_flag, review_flag, top_flag, ad_flag, delete_flag, recommend_flag, keyword, status, delete_no, delete_name, delete_time, add_no, add_name, add_time, update_no, update_name, update_time) VALUES (13, '俄罗斯新增9268例新冠肺炎确诊病例 累计超40万例', '（原标题：俄罗斯新增确诊病例9268例 成为全球第3个确诊超40万国家）', 3, null, '', '<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 18px; line-height: 32px; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; text-indent: 2em; color: #404040; text-align: justify; background-color: #ffffff;"><span style="font-weight: bold; font-family: SimSun; text-align: start; text-indent: 28px;">【海外网5月31日|战疫全时区】</span>据俄罗斯新冠病毒防疫官网31日最新数据，过去24小时，俄罗斯新增9268例新冠肺炎确诊病例，累计确诊405843例，成为全球第3个确诊超40万国家；新增死亡病例138例，累计死亡病例4693例。</p>
