<h1 style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 36px; line-height: 1; font-family: ''Microsoft Yahei''; color: #404040;">仝卓自曝高考身份造假：究竟用了什么手段？</h1>
<div class="post_time_source" style="margin-top: 20px; font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 1; font-family: Arial, ''Sim sun''; color: #888888;">2020-05-31 12:56:48　来源:&nbsp;<a id="ne_article_source" style="color: #888888;" href="http://society.people.com.cn/n1/2020/0530/c428181-31729816.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">人民网</a><a class="post_jubao" style="color: #888888; float: right; margin-left: 14px; padding-right: 10px; padding-left: 18px; background-image: url(''https://img0.ph.126.net/qMUyvLBlNVnwQ7QZWJfCQQ==/6631769254118984670.png''); background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;" title="举报" href="http://jubao.aq.163.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">举报</a></div>
